Your Available Data Tables
Based on your dbt models:

Dimension Tables:
marts.dim_date - Date dimension with day/week/month
marts.dim_station - Station details
marts.dim_time - Time of day dimension
marts.dim_user_type - Member vs Casual
Fact Tables:
marts.fct_trips - Trip-level data (grain: one row per trip)
marts.fct_station_day - Station daily metrics (grain: one row per station per day)
Staging Tables (if needed):
staging.stg_trips - Cleaned trip data
staging.stg_weather - Weather observations
staging.stg_station_status - Station status snapshots
Pro Tips
1. Use Blended Data
Combine multiple tables:

Join fct_trips with dim_station for station names
Join fct_station_day with dim_date for date attributes
2. Add Filters
Date range picker
Station selector
User type filter (Member/Casual)
3. Create Calculated Fields
Trip Duration (minutes) = trip_duration_seconds / 60
Utilization Rate = trips_started / capacity
Revenue per Trip = total_revenue / trip_count

txt


4. Schedule Email Reports
Click "Share" → "Schedule email delivery"
Set frequency (daily, weekly)
Add recipients
5. Embed in Websites
Click "Share" → "Embed report"
Copy iframe code
Paste in your website/app
